article_title: Planned Parenthood Supports Over-The-Counter Birth Control, But Only Alongside Obamacare's Contraceptive Mandate

article_metadata.author: Capital Flows

og.description: By JOHN C. JENNINGS and VANESSA CULLINS - Planned Parenthood has extensively supported increased availability of birth control, including through over-the-counter access. But over-the-counter access alone is not a suitable replacement for no-copay birth control coverage.
